title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-26-2013 THURS
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-26-2013 THURS .............PODCAST






The Glenn Beck Program




Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


        
      
The Glenn Beck Program - 12/26/13Thursday, December 26, 2013 10:51 AM


Mike Broomhead fills in for Glenn and he talks beliefs and our culture,

     as he weighs in on the Phil Robertson situation with Duck Dynasty.

      Also, Mike drops a bomb with new information on the Fast and Furious scandal
 
         and how federal agents could have cost border patrol lives.


  Plus, a Christmas message from Edward Snowden, and it's one that makes a lot of sense.
